==Calculating Large Caliber Fit==
The formula for fit bonuses is:<br>
<math>\text{Fit Bonus}_\text{Ship} = \sum \text{Fit Bonus}_\text{Gun} \times \sqrt{\text{Number of Guns Equipped}}</math>

An example:
Kongou having 2 35.6cm and 1 46cm.<br>
Fit Bonus: (7 x √2) + (-10 x √1) = -0.1

