==Italian Heavy Cruiser Fit Bonus==
[[Zara]] and [[Pola]] a further firepower fit bonus when equipped with the [[203mm / 53 Twin Gun Mount]]. In addition to the flat '''+1 accuracy''' bonus, the firepower bonus is calculated using the following formula:

<math>\text{Italian Gun Fit Bonus} = \sqrt{\text{No of Guns}}</math>

This firepower bonus is '''pre-cap'''.

