===Calculating Firepower Bonus===
The formula for the firepower bonus is:<br>
<math>\text{Fit bonus} = (2  \times \sqrt{\text{No of Twin Guns}}) + \sqrt{\text{No of Single Guns}}</math>

Example calculation:
A light cruiser with 1 15.2cm Twin and 2 15.2cm Singles<br>
Firepower bonus: (2 × √1) + √2 = 3.4

